sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Orch as 任务编排
    participant DBCat as DBCat
    participant Full as FullImport
    participant Store as Store
    participant Incr as IncrSync
    participant Verify as FullVerification

    User->>Orch: 创建并启动迁移任务
    Orch->>Orch: 预检查
    Orch->>DBCat: 结构迁移
    DBCat-->>Orch: Schema完成
    Orch->>Full: 全量迁移
    Full-->>Orch: 全量完成并记录位点
    Orch->>Store: 启动增量拉取
    Orch->>Incr: 启动增量同步
    Incr-->>Orch: 延迟降至阈值
    Orch->>Verify: 数据校验
    Verify-->>Orch: 校验通过
    Orch->>User: 可执行业务切换
